column10: Hi! My name is Carlos. I have owned Flowers By Carlos on Valencia and Dubuce for almost 20 years. We are a family owned local business as I run the shop with my wife and my son. I am interested in both utilizing Ad Collab to promote my business and also interested in leasing out the wall space on the north-facing side of my shop.

Hello! My name is Sheyna. I own a thift shop on the corner of 14th and Valencia- across the street from the Chase bank and next to the Flower Market Grocery. I am very interested in leasing out the back wall of my building as it has plenty of space to leverage for local patrons. Send in a Request if you're interested!
